== Derivative Work Notice ==

This is a derivative work (fork) of Google's Gemini CLI. The following
modifications have been made:

- Added OpenAI-compatible API support, enabling use with any LLM provider
  (on-prem vLLM, Ollama, OpenAI, Anthropic, OpenRouter, etc.)
- Replaced the Google authentication prompt with a model picker UI
- Added a JSON-based model registry (models.default.json) for configuring
  LLM endpoints without code changes
- Added Langfuse integration for on-prem LLM observability/tracing
- Added a Python helper (scripts/fork/gemini_llm.py) for LangChain integration
- Various bug fixes for streaming tool calls, token handling, and
  multi-provider compatibility

Modified files in the original codebase carry "// [FORK]" comments.
Fork-specific files are listed in CLAUDE.md.

